'''Turza takrurant''' neɣ '''Tuqqna takrurant''' deg [[takrura|tekrura]] d [[tumant]] n tuṭṭfa d tdukla n [[abelkim|ibelkimen]] deg [[Acubar|ucubar]] 
Tuqqniwin tikruranin yakk ttuɣalent ar [[asedmer|usedmer]] ar n [[Aliktṛun|iliktrunen]] yellan deg [[abelkim|ubelkim]], Dɣa iliktrunen-a d amur seg [[amezzay abelkam|umezzay abelkam]], Maca deg turza neɣ tuqqna iliktrunen gellund s [[amezzay acubran|umezzay acubran]] gar n sin n ibelkimen neɣ ugar

